{"tid":175963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心急男尖沙咀追巴士遭撞斃　警拉的士司機","createTime":"2017-03-28T00:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T09:14:43.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f67a30b99a7e8adeb4358a804c0325151d1561b","tid":175963,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:31:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>心急男尖沙咀追巴士遭撞斃　警拉的士司機</strong><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀發生奪命交通意外，凌晨零時許，一名69歲姓曾男子，於彌敦道近海防道交界行人輔助線跑過馬路，其時一輛的士沿彌敦道中線往深水埗方向駛至，右邊車頭將曾撞至拋起，撼及擋風玻璃反彈落地，倒臥約10米外路面，頭部重創昏迷，地上遺下一攤血漬；救護員到場將曾送院，惜搶救逾1個小時後傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的士右邊車頭損毀，姓羅61歲司機在場協助了解，警員經初步調查，懷疑事主追趕巴士期間遇到車禍，羅涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人死亡，被帶署扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，曾與妻子住沙田，事發前在尖沙咀與友人相聚，其後準備前往乘車回家，詎料遭逢車禍。"},{"pid":"5bb5c8b901478c6dbbf53e989ea36d9b68c7bd61","tid":175963,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:32:30.000Z","msg":"趕住投胎就係呢啲喇"},{"pid":"bc5d36fd0d9b6f181648ba38e1ae75449c7a6678","tid":175963,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:33:05.000Z","msg":"個的士司機好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b21a6a9c7e0d5d694a30a22c8f249792f6f685","tid":175963,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>趕住投胎就係呢啲喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3312048ae0aea58c7ba2f9831666bb0b3287f46e","tid":175963,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個的士司機好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dd38a532e01f389badce9177e54633c0b2c572","tid":175963,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>趕住投胎就係呢啲喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n趕住返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b161269f704f1a9d32910ea14e8993bf31b73de0","tid":175963,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個架的士<del>司機</del>好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdbccd2136e6e66a0642d21f1ba9e7fd8845c95","tid":175963,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:44:45.000Z","msg":"廢老<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n累人"},{"pid":"64b82fce3ef9146c0b95147080a01502f50826a2","tid":175963,"uid":25656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02a759325789a397d44fef763d2198cc0be92a8","tid":175963,"uid":3409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"好痛心 呢件事無論邊個岩邊個錯都好 你地班職業司機可唔可以揸車小心d啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fafa810ae5ae30963a0deeacc0acf75c87c321c","tid":175963,"uid":3409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"點解仲未有大愛撚入黎屌7個的士佬<br />\n因為呢次撞死嘅唔係學生妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6e7fa8bb512ebab7e31190d1d9f9e9b57c16a3","tid":175963,"uid":9930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:56:43.000Z","msg":"煞唔切車撞死人抵拉啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e21aa8bbb8f9f04b2b91e4aa0f37505c0bf25b2","tid":175963,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"阿伯死就無人理<br />\n15歲學生妹就叫人積厚德<br />\n成班咸濕仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj